com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.embedded

Interface IFIXListenerCallback

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IStatefulFIXListenerCallback
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmbeddedAdapterInboundLatencyBenchmark, EmbeddedAdapterOutboundLatencyBenchmark, EmbeddedAdapterStatelessRouterBenchmark, EmbeddedCatalysNodeAdapterQueuedListener, EmbeddedCatalysNodeAdapterUnqueuedListener

    public interface IFIXListenerCallback
    Interface which defines the events delivered by the IFIXSourceProxy to registered listeners.

    This interface is a narrowing of IFIXListener.

      • onMessageFromFix

        void onMessageFromFix(MessageEvent event,
                      IFIXMessage message)
               throws IOException,
                      MissingDataException,
                      ConversionException
        FIX Message received from FIX session.

        Can throw a MessageProcessorRejectException containing a FIX message which will be sent out over FIX by way of a "reject".

        Parameters:
        event - the event
        message - the message
        Throws:
        IOException - if an exception occurs when processing the message
        MissingDataException - if an exception occurs when processing the message
        ConversionException - if an exception occurs when processing the message
        See Also:
        IFIXListener.onMessageFromFix(com.camerontec.catalys.util.messaging.MessageEvent, com.camerontec.catalys.core.message.IFIXMessage)
